{"about_the_game":"Steel Effigy is a third person action-roguelite, hack n slash, set in a Steampunk world. Wield several combat defining weapons simultaneously and imbue them with elemental augments to enhance their power. Create unique builds by collecting and using powerful items, augments and abilities to help you defeat the hordes of soulless machines under the control of The Barons, a group of powerful leaders in control of a tyrannical government. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903980/extras/LightningSpinGif.gif?t=1721139335\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903980/extras/Steam_Titles_01.png?t=1721139335\" /><br><br>Choose your loadout of weapons from a vast pool of unique weapons, that each have their own strengths. Customize these weapons mid run with powerful passives and elemental augments to burn, freeze, electrocute or send enemies flying.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903980/extras/Weapons_Gif.gif?t=1721139335\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903980/extras/Steam_Titles_02.png?t=1721139335\" /><br><br>Collect powerful items to bring down lightning storms, unleash fiery explosions, summon ice golems and even use the power of gravity to decimate enemies. Through random drops, you gain access to different items every run and with the abilities able to combo with one another, every run will have you playing with new and diverse builds.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903980/extras/CombatGif_Weapon_Swap.gif?t=1721139335\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2903980/extras/Steam_Titles_03.png?t=1721139335\" /><br><br>Unlock new we